translation: O the Preserver Lord! O Salvation-Giver Lord! O Most Genereous Lord! O Boundless Lord! 94.
O Destroyer Lord! O the Creator Lord! O the Nameless Lord! O the Desireless Lord! 95.

gurmukhi: ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਕਰਤਾ ॥ ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਹਰਤਾ ॥
transliteration: Chattra Chakkra Kartaa|| Chattra Chakkra Hartaa||
translation: O the Creator Lord of all the four directions. O the Destroyer Lord of the four directions.

gurmukhi: ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਦਾਨੇ ॥ ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਜਾਨੇ ॥੯੬॥
transliteration: Chattra Chakkra Daane|| Chattra Chakkra Jaane||96||
translation: O the Donor Lord of all the four directions. O the Known Lord of all the four directions.96.

gurmukhi: ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਵਰਤੀ ॥ ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਭਰਤੀ ॥
transliteration: Chattra Chakkra Vartoo|| Chattra Chakkra Bhartoo||
translation: O the Pervading Lord of the four directions. O the Permeator Lord of all the four direction.

gurmukhi: ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਪਾਲੇ ॥ ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਕਾਲੇ ॥੯੭॥
transliteration: Chattra Chakkra Paale|| Chattra Chakkra Kaale||97||
translation: O the Sustainer Lord of all the four directions. O the Destroyer Lord of all the four directions.97.

gurmukhi: ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਪਾਸੇ ॥ ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਵਾਸੇ ॥
transliteration: Chattra Chakkra Paase|| Chattra Chakkra Vaase||
translation: O the Lord Present in all the four direction. O the Dweller Lord in all the four directions.

gurmukhi: ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਮਾਨÎੈ ॥ ਚੱਤ੍ਰੁ ਚੱਕ੍ਰ, ਦਾਨÎੈ ॥੯੮॥
transliteration: Chattra Chakkra Maanyai|| Chattra Chakkra Daanyai||98||
translation: O the Lord Worshipped in all the four directions. O the Donor Lord of all the four directions.98.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਸੱਤ੍ਰੈ ॥ ਨ ਮਿੱਤ੍ਰੈ ॥ ਨ ਭਰਮੰ ॥ ਨ ਭਿੱਤ੍ਰੈ ॥੯੯॥
transliteration: Na Sattrai|| Na Mittrai|| Na Bharman|| Na Bhittrai||99||
translation: Thou art the Foeless Lord, Thou art the Friendless Lord, Thou art the Illusionless Lord, Thou art the Fearless Lord.99.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਕਰਮੰ ॥ ਨ ਕਾੲੇ ॥ ਅਜਨਮੰ ॥ ਅਜਾੲੇ ॥੧੦੦॥
transliteration: Na Karamannd|| Na Kaae|| Ajanamannd|| Ajaae||100||
translation: Thou art the Actionless Lord, Thou art the Bodyless Lord, Thu art the Birthless Lord, Thou art the Aboleless Lord.100.

transliteration: Na Chittrai|| Na Mittrai|| Para Hain|| Pavittrai||101||
translation: Thou art the Portrait-less Lord, Thou art the Friendliness Lord, Thou art the Attachment-free Lord, Thou art the Most Pure Lord.101.
Thou art the World-Master Lord, Thou art the Primal Lord, Thou art the Primal Lord, Thou art the Invincible Lord, Thou art the Almighty Lord.102.
